the dragon gate is a 1933 american pre-code drama film directed by lloyd bacon and written by robert &lt;unk&gt; . the film stars sessue hayakawa , tsuru aoki , lorna gray , robert lowery , felix aylmer , robert lowery , felix bressart , lloyd whitlock , and lee &lt;unk&gt; . the film was released on december 1 , 1940 , by republic pictures .